  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study was to compare the subthalamic nucleus(STN) with the globus
      pallidus internus(GPi) as a stimulation target for deep brian stimulation(DBS) for medically
      refractory dystonia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      In this prospective randomized controlled study,elecrodes were bilaterally implanted in STN
      and Gpi of 40 patients with dystonia.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
